      • isChildOperation

        boolean isChildOperation​(Operation op)
                  throws ScimException
        Tests whether the current operation depends on the operation supplied (is a predicate).
        Parameters:
        op - An Operation value that should execute before the current one.
        Returns:
        True if the operation is defined as a predicate operation.
        Throws:
        ScimException - may be thrown when a SCIM error occurs (not a child?)

      • getJsonReplicaOp

        com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode getJsonReplicaOp()
        Generates a bulk request "operation" for the operation performed. Used to propagate replication ops. Note that for request, the post-add result is sent to capture generated "id".
        Returns:
        A JsonNode representation of operation in Bulk "Operation" format as described in RFC7644 Sec 3.7. If the operation did not complete normally, the request returns NULL (because the operation was not processed).
